txt.en: Defeat all of the Jephai Corsairs within The Streets of Râhal Bakh
Defeat all of the Jephai Corsairs within The Streets of Râhal Bakh.
The Streets of Râhal Bakh -- Braver
Khâshap and his Jephai have run rampant in the streets for far too long. You must defeat all of the Jephai in The Streets of Râhal Bakh and rid the Umbari of their influence and corruption.
